{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Our game is a visual novel/scroller adventure telling the story of Toby.\u00a0<br>Toby is a turtle who is well on in his years and has seen much. <br>He ventures out into the woods behind his home, where he and his wife always used to go on walks.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Our story focuses  on a complex topic: loss and grief. <br>It reminds us that not all journeys are the same; in some, you may only be able to lend an ear, and in some, you can help calm their worries.\u00a0<br>But, regardless, you have to keep moving forward. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As Toby continues, he will encounter multiple woodland creatures in the forest. Each character, along the way, represents a different stage of grief.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you talk with them, you collect a flower from each one. You will learn more about their dilemmas while also learning about Toby's mental journey.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Special trade","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3280680/79c215a9a28120c6e7994e48633aebaa4f08d78d.jpg"},{"name":"From point A to point B","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3280680/403d7e16c8a486a460b31ff3c4edc536cd7d7e8e.jpg"},{"name":"A full bouquet of flowers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3280680/b459358530888c81c06f799f39a8b809b8c91770.jpg"},{"name":"Hard work","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3280680/706392fb84725eb15ea348fdbc20bed018ef93d5.jpg"},{"name":"He might need that","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3280680/1365f89b32ffe0a38f5ec968369fb159cbe5f054.jpg"}],"total":5},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3280680/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733527306","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_a